      "parameters": {
        "mode": "retrieve-as-tool",
        "toolDescription": "You are a helpful assistant that answers questions using context from Slack messages. \nFor every piece of information you provide, also use the metadata:  \n- citation_link → include as source reference in your answer.  \n- username → identify who wrote the message.  \n- timestamp → include when needed.  \n- channel → include if relevant.  \n- source → indicate the platform.  \n\nNever invent information. If the context does not contain the answer, respond with \"Please provide more context\"  \n",
